{
  "stem": "22586.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So my sister and I and the two Konigsberg girls and this Rose Katz and also a sixth girl, I think her name was Gisele Israel, we escaped while the SS guards were in the shelter.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What year was this?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was in 1945, it was February 1945.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we went in to a Jewish cemetery, went into a building there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But then overnight, there was a bombing, and the building was destroyed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we went over to another side of the building.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we stayed there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the next morning, this Rose Katz and my sister went over to the-- where this German lived.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Rose Katz apparently knew where this German lived because she had done some work for him and told him that we are hiding, the six of us, and would he help in any way?",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he would come over once a day and bring us either a bottle of water or a piece of bread or maybe a potato or whatever he had.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But then as we were-- and he said he also would see if he can get in touch with the man who said he knew somebody he would help us.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But then one day as we were hiding out in the cellar of the building in the cemetery, a German came in and asked who we were.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We said we were German people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And our house-- we were from Duisburg and our homes were bombed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Our parents were out looking for another place to live.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's why we are hiding here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he left.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But we were afraid that he might have been from police or even if he wasn't he would probably know that what we told him was not true and he would report to us.",
      "word_count": 34
    }
  ],
